WEBVTT

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:44.520
Get out!

00:00:47.320 --> 00:00:48.200
Young master.

00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:52.080
Please talk to the master.

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:15.720
Wake up.

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:18.800
Wake up.

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:23.440
Father, it's time to get up.

00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:46.770
I've failed you as a son.

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:51.680
You scold me.

00:01:55.039 --> 00:01:56.080
You hit me.

00:01:58.080 --> 00:01:59.000
Hit me.

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:00.120
Hit me.

00:02:01.240 --> 00:02:03.000
Hit me. Hit me.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:08.360
Hit me.

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.880
I'll hit myself.

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:12.080
Silin.

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:26.560
Silin.

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:28.400
I'll hit myself.

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:30.000
Father, get up and hit me.

00:02:30.040 --> 00:02:32.500
Young master, your wounds have just healed.

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:34.340
Please don't get too excited.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:35.760
Young master.

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:36.560
Father.

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:38.760
Silin.

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:40.280
Take him away.

00:02:40.600 --> 00:02:41.400
Young master.

00:02:42.079 --> 00:02:42.880
Young master.

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:47.280
Get up and hit me.

00:02:55.160 --> 00:02:56.360
All of you, leave now.

00:02:57.160 --> 00:02:58.820
Let me be alone with my father.

00:03:34.440 --> 00:03:35.280
Father.

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:39.200
Can you hear me?

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:44.160
You've never cared about me your entire life.

00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:48.079
Just because of my humble origins.

00:03:48.920 --> 00:03:51.120
I've been looked down upon everywhere.

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:56.000
While that madman Liu Silin has done so many outrageous things.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:03:59.460
Yet you've always been lenient with him.

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:02.520
He even dreams of replacing me as your heir.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.920
Do you think as a father,

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:10.200
you deserve that title?

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:17.360
My dear father.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:21.560
I won't let you and Liu Silin succeed.

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:25.000
Do you know how much effort I've put in

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:26.920
to reach this position?

00:04:34.080 --> 00:04:35.140
It doesn't matter.

00:04:36.080 --> 00:04:37.800
You won't need to know anyway.

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.280
Because,

00:04:41.280 --> 00:04:42.280
today,

00:04:44.920 --> 00:04:46.440
you're going to die.

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:53.200
You probably don't know,

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:56.280
that in your daily meals,

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.200
I've been poisoning you.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:02.440
So your health hasn't improved,

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:05.530
but has gotten worse and worse.

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:09.240
But,

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:14.520
is all this my fault?

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:20.680
Is it my fault?

00:05:23.960 --> 00:05:25.960
Blame yourself.

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:29.680
It's your own favoritism.

00:05:31.840 --> 00:05:33.570
You deserve this retribution.

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:51.520
Master.

00:06:52.080 --> 00:06:53.240
Where is the young master?

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:57.500
The young master is still locking himself in his room and refuses to come out.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:06.960
Brother.

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.280
Brother.

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:15.280
Father has been gone for over a month now.

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:17.680
Brother, you need to pull yourself together.

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:19.960
The Liu family has so many affairs waiting to be managed.

00:07:19.960 --> 00:07:23.680
I can't handle everything alone.

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:33.280
Do you know what the elders in the family are saying about you?

00:07:33.280 --> 00:07:34.480
What are they saying?

00:07:36.840 --> 00:07:38.570
Never mind. It's not pleasant.

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:40.120
I'd better not say it.

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:41.240
Tell me.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:44.280
What can't you say?

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:49.120
They all say the master raised a useless son.

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:50.840
A coward.

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:53.560
Who only causes trouble when he's not having fits.

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:56.840
The master was probably angered to death by him.

00:07:58.120 --> 00:07:59.840
Say that again.

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:03.200
I said I wouldn't tell you, but you insisted.

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:04.240
I told you.

00:08:04.440 --> 00:08:07.080
Now you're upset and can't accept it.

00:08:11.400 --> 00:08:12.840
Let me tell you.

00:08:13.840 --> 00:08:16.500
Father's death must not be as simple as it seems.

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:19.240
I will find out the truth about everything.

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:20.280
Brother.

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:22.840
Face reality.

00:08:23.200 --> 00:08:24.720
Father used to protect you.

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:25.920
But now

00:08:26.640 --> 00:08:29.640
you're like a stray dog with no home.

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:35.280
Just look at yourself now.

00:08:35.840 --> 00:08:37.100
If you're not useless,

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.240
then what are you?

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:44.120
You.

00:09:06.520 --> 00:09:07.240
â€”Yu.

00:09:09.560 --> 00:09:10.440
Yiyu.

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:16.480
Young Master Liu manages everything in the Liu family. You're extremely busy.

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:18.280
How do you have time to come here?

00:09:18.320 --> 00:09:20.600
Yiyu, I came specifically to see you.

00:09:20.720 --> 00:09:22.050
Are you feeling better?

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:24.080
Please don't trouble yourself worrying about me, Young Master.

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:24.960
Yiyu.

00:09:25.640 --> 00:09:26.880
I've finally made it.

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:30.130
Now I'm in charge of everything in the Liu household.

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:32.900
Do you remember the promise I made to you?

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:34.840
Promise.

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:38.520
I promised you.

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:41.700
Once I take control of the Liu family.

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:43.400
I'll be with you.

00:09:49.080 --> 00:09:50.080
Have you

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:53.200
really fallen for Liu Silin?

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:56.570
Don't come looking for me unless it's important.

00:09:57.200 --> 00:09:58.400
Liu Silin is just a madman.

00:09:58.400 --> 00:09:59.720
He's finished.

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:01.520
He lost his father.

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:03.400
He's like a pile of mud.

00:10:03.520 --> 00:10:05.780
Do you still want to be with him like this?

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:07.200
Liu Sinan.

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:11.560
Although you're now the head of the Liu family,

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:14.160
Silin is still your elder brother.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:16.480
So please show him respect.

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:19.280
Also,

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:22.160
where I go is none of your business.

00:10:22.280 --> 00:10:23.960
So please leave now.

00:10:25.400 --> 00:10:27.640
Our positions are different now.

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:30.420
It wouldn't look good if others saw us together.

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:16.840
Silin, please eat something.

00:11:26.400 --> 00:11:27.320
Silin.

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:30.560
If you continue not eating or drinking for a month,

00:11:30.960 --> 00:11:32.720
look how worn out you've become.

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:34.080
If this continues,

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:36.720
the master won't rest in peace.

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:40.320
All the servants have left.

00:11:41.520 --> 00:11:43.960
Why haven't you left?

00:11:44.960 --> 00:11:47.320
Why should I leave?

00:11:48.280 --> 00:11:50.640
I'm the wife of the Liu family's eldest son.

00:11:50.640 --> 00:11:52.970
You follow your husband wherever he goes.

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:01.840
Listen to me.

00:12:02.960 --> 00:12:05.280
The master is gone. That's a fact.

00:12:05.640 --> 00:12:08.080
But you can't keep wasting away like this.

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:11.520
Liu Sinan now controls the entire Liu family.

00:12:11.720 --> 00:12:13.780
I heard from people at the restaurant

00:12:14.280 --> 00:12:17.210
that he's often associating with shady characters.

00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:20.130
Who knows what kind of business he's involved in.

00:12:21.160 --> 00:12:23.080
You're the eldest son of the Liu family.

00:12:23.080 --> 00:12:24.600
You can't just stand by

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:27.400
and watch him destroy the Liu family.

00:12:30.080 --> 00:12:31.080
But I...

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:34.600
I have nothing left now.

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:35.720
No!

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:37.400
You have me.

00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:39.720
And you still have the Fulu Restaurant.

